{"tid":511944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前「熱血公民」成員李政熙去年選舉論壇外襲警判囚7周","createTime":"2017-12-28T03:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T03:48:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c83948051c58cd95755ed4e19b4922b1bfcd0533","tid":511944,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1372208-20171228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1372208-20171228.htm&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2FZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=086471ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1372208-20171228.htm&h=5136efbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1372208-20171228.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1372208_1_20171228113138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1372208_1_20171228113138.jpg&h=4c241dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前「熱血公民」成員李政熙去年於九龍西立法會選舉論壇結束後，在場外有爭執，有兩名警員被襲擊。他早前被裁定兩項襲警罪成立，在九龍城裁判法院被判監7星期。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師求情時指，被告當時沒有使用武器，兩位警員亦無大礙，考慮到被告沒有案底以及有正當職業，將來重犯的可能性非常低，希望法官輕判。<br />\n<br />\n暫委裁判官馬漢璋表示，警方當時只是執行職務及維持社會秩序和安全，襲警案件性質嚴重，需要判處阻嚇性懲罰，考慮到被告沒有刑事案底，判處7星期監禁。"},{"pid":"516aa2c6e2c9c0c50c44bcb13eca509634a1ab9e","tid":511944,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"熱狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe7a71253540e6c59558bd3aea5a23976820e27","tid":511944,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"已割~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 安心上路"}]}